NOTE ON THE COMPILED BINARY (GudhiCore.xcframework)

This MIT license covers the original source in this repository (the facade /
Swift wrapper code). The prebuilt GudhiCore.xcframework (main/permissive build)
statically links only permissively licensed third-party libraries (GUDHI MIT,
Boost BSL-1.0, Hera BSD), so the binary as a whole is permissive and may be used
in closed-source applications. See THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md.

A separate GPL-3.0 "full" build (adding CGAL/GMP/MPFR-backed Alpha, Tangential,
Euclidean Witness and sparsify) lives on the `full-gpl` branch.
